{
  "id": "adv_event_2504_02_03",
  "title": "ザグラとバルゴの過去",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時空の狭間が閉じるまであと9時間",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—9 Hours Until the Space-Time Rift Closes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 2.2666666786,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_watch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "『モーター』が手に入りましたわ～！\nこれで壊れてる所は、もうなさそうですわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve obtained the “Motor”~!\nIt looks like there’s nothing broken anymore!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1333333452,
      "endTime": 9.642585225800001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 9.8559183875
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "後は燃料とかかな？　ここまで順調だね！\nこの調子で、次の謎を探すぞ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe all that’s left is fuel? We’ve come this far without a hitch!\nLet’s keep this momentum and find the next riddle~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8559183875,
      "endTime": 18.1559183875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "よし、残るはあと『エネルギー』だけだ！\n次のヒントは……あれ？　このペン書けないぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All right‚ the only thing left is “Energy”!\nThe next hint is… huh? This pen won’t write?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3625838715,
      "endTime": 28.2370734649,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 49.87185879999956
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 49.87185879999956
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ゲーシゲシゲシ！\nまたかかったゲシな、{user}！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geee-shi geshi geshi!\nYou fell for it again‚ {user}‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4304065504,
      "endTime": 33.2704081812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "ゴドノ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Godono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "フフ……聞いて驚かないでおくれ。実は……\n星見プロ中のボールペンのキャップを外しておいたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu… don’t be too shocked when you hear this. In fact…\nI removed the caps from every ballpoint pen in Hoshimi Pro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4637414096,
      "endTime": 44.023265278299995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なっ……！　そんなの、インクがカピカピになって\n使えなくなるじゃないか！　どうしてそんなことを！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha—!? Then the ink will dry out\nand they’ll become unusable! Why would you do that!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1304101108,
      "endTime": 51.5077798008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "ズミレ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "自分が一番心当たりあるんとちゃいますか？\nあんちゃん……さっきから怪しい行動してるやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ain’t you the one who should know best why?\nBro… you’ve been acting suspicious this whole time‚ haven’t ya?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.721112867,
      "endTime": 61.1744441467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "ビボ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Bibo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "実はさ～さっきこっそりそいつのポッケ縫い付けて\n開かないようにしてたら、偶然聞いちゃったんだけど～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ like‚ I secretly stitched his pocket shut earlier\nso it wouldn’t open~‚ and I just happened to overhear~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.3877774992,
      "endTime": 69.2677774229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "ビボ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Bibo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "こいつ、さくら達と通信してたんだよ！？\nマシンがどうとか……マジありえなくない！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He was communicating with Sakura and the others!?\nSomething about a machine… like‚ seriously‚ isn’t that insane!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4544441658,
      "endTime": 77.08778147279999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なっ！　勝手にポケットにイタズラしてたのか！？\nくっ……卑怯な！　小さいから気付けないじゃないか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? You messed with my pocket without permission!?\nUgh… that’s dirty! You’re so small I couldn’t even notice!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2877815682,
      "endTime": 85.65394939970001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "ゴドノ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Godono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "フフ……だが、マシンのことを知っているのは\n私達だけ……この中に裏切り者がいるってことになるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu… but only we should know about the machine.\nWhich means there must be a traitor among us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.867282466,
      "endTime": 97.0739496985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "ズズ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zuzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ユルセナイ……\nウラギリモノ、ツブス……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unforgivable…\nTraitor… crush…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.2672829746,
      "endTime": 102.73333131070001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "ガナ！　お前、ミボとブランに会いたくて\n泣いていたゲシな！？　怪しいゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gana! You were crying because you wanted to see Mibo and Bran‚\nweren’t you‚ geshi!? Suspicious‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.0006152907,
      "endTime": 110.28061054140001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "ガナ",
      "speakerNameEn": "gana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ひ、ひぃっ！　ミボちゃんとブランちゃんに\n会いたいのは本当だけど、私何もしてませんよぉ～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "E-eek! It’s true I want to see Mibo-chan and Bran-chan‚\nbut I didn’t do anything~!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4672773797,
      "endTime": 119.3339477977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "うるさいゲシ！　ガナはてるてる坊主の刑にするゲシ！\n早くこっちに来るゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Quiet‚ geshi! Gana‚ you’re sentenced to the “teru-teru bozu” punishment‚ geshi!\nGet over here‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.5339476069,
      "endTime": 126.1406101664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "バルゴ！　また怪しい動きが出来ないように\nポケットで見張っておくゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Barugo! Make sure he can’t make any suspicious moves again—\nkeep watch from inside the pocket‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.333943538,
      "endTime": 132.3606164733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（くそ……バルゴに見張られていて、うかつに動けない）\n（時空の狭間はどんどん閉じていくし、どうすれば……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Damn… with Barugo watching me‚ I can’t move carelessly.）\n（And the rift is closing more and more… what should I do…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.00061936,
      "endTime": 143.5648825131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Barugo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "見張りになれて好都合YOYO！\n次のヒントの場所を教えるエイヨー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being the lookout works out perfectly‚ YO YO!\nI’ll tell you where the next hint is‚ ayo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.75154897,
      "endTime": 149.4248819473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　ヒントって……もしかして\nバルゴさんが俺達を助けてくれてたんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? The hint… could it be—\nBarugo-san‚ have you been helping us!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.618215128,
      "endTime": 156.18760285000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりバルゴさんだったのか……！\n思ったより単純……いや、裏の裏をかいたんですよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So it really was you…!\nSimpler than I thought… No‚ you were thinking two steps ahead!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.4009360117,
      "endTime": 163.5793959421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Barugo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "大声NG、お前に教示。ストレートには言えないけれど\n次のヒントは『チラシ配り』　レッツゴー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No loud voices—here’s the tip. I can’t say it straight‚ but…\nThe next hint is “handing out flyers.” Let’s go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.7660624943,
      "endTime": 172.14606241799999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "バルゴさん、どうして俺達にそこまで……？\nザグラ達にバレたら、大変なことになるんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Barugo-san‚ why go this far for us…?\nIf Zagura finds out‚ won’t it be terrible for you…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.332729161,
      "endTime": 179.5393978241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Barugo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "ザグラ達は元々善人！　昔はともに目指すトップ\nアイドル！　厳しい芸能界に揉まれ変化！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Zagura and the others were good people once! We used to aim\nfor the top idols together! But the harsh entertainment world changed them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.7527311765,
      "endTime": 187.4593879185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なんだって！？　ザグラとバルゴさんも昔は\n凄く仲が良くてまっすぐなアイドルだったんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? So you and Zagura were once\nclose friends and straightforward idols!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.652721004,
      "endTime": 194.4382313534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことか……バルゴさんも、昔のザグラに戻って\n欲しいってことなんですね……！　ぐすっ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… you want Zagura to go back to\nhow she used to be…! sniff…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.7382372661,
      "endTime": 203.5143601222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
